sed '/^$/d' file.txt  -- for deleting all the blank lines of this file
ls *.pdf *.txt - it will list all the files ending with pdf and txt
ls -I "*.pdf" -I "*.txt" - it will list all the files except ending with pdf and txt
ls | sed  -e 's/file1.txt/file1.jpg/g' - it will replace file1 with jpg

